{"type": "article", "id": 16874, "title": "小胖 Alber 为 Lanvin 忙活了 14 年， 他的迷人作品你值得一看", "description": "观赏愉快。", "date": "2015-11-01T08:36:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8, "name": "奢侈品"}, {"id": 18072, "name": "创意总监"}, {"id": 12089, "name": "女装"}, {"id": 15919, "name": "浪漫"}, {"id": 18073, "name": "百褶"}, {"id": 7797, "name": "秀场"}, {"id": 2528, "name": "离职"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 206, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021240438n9sdxgrT2LpA6eF.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t即使是在时尚界这样永恒追求快速变迁的领域，最近的变动也未免有些惊人，如果说“多事之秋”里 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/12793.html\" target=\"_blank\">Alexander Wang 卸任 Balenciaga </a>还在预料之中；<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/16543.html\" target=\"_blank\">Raf Simon 离开 Dior</a> 的决定开始令人措手不及；那么 2001 年就加入 Lanvin 任职创意总监的 Alber Elbaz，出走的消息就像一枚重磅炸弹。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t14 年前，当时经营不善几经转手的法国奢侈品牌 Lanvin 被台湾报业女强人王效兰买下，找来 Alber 扛起设计大旗，这位天才设计师果然没让人失望，他的华丽、浪漫设计叫好又叫座，连 Anna Wintour 都称他为“世界三大顶级设计师之一”。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124029XMzwbETQi1FIUjfD.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"719\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t而在这一消息公布的前一周里，Alber 在 Fashion Group International 之夜的庆典上从梅丽尔 ·斯特里普（Meryl Streep）手上接过 “The Revolutionaries – Super Star”的奖杯，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/alber-elbaz-said-to-exit-lanvin-10269858/\" target=\"_blank\">获奖感言</a>颇有离职前奏的意味。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t他说（截取大意）：“过去我们的初衷是思考女人想要什么、需要什么，能做点什么让女人更美丽。然而如今的创意总监除了创造，更多是指导，确保这衣服能拍出好看的照片，确保屏幕上显示得好看。喧嚣的事开始变酷，但我更喜欢更深刻、更持久的低语。”\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t我们整理了过去的 14 年中他在 Lanvin 的经典设计。有趣的是，当年注重秀场照片的人远没有现在这么多，所以，你得忍受一下像素越来越低的照片：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124030a5BcENIg307jRTYV.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"542\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2016 春季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124030QE1uWOV2SMCdI86Y.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124031ba3HG8nxqIBkdr1o.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2015 秋季<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124031ldRCSk5abXnqIe86.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2015 度假系列\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124032OKZQHoJL2aXcnDq9.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"542\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124032h9ZYKf1kOHxEwUDe.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2015 春季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124033uMPDVjG8LvN9sOCl.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:justify;\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\">2014早秋／秋季系列</span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124033KfzYpy5hi9B0T3Ib.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2014度假／春季系列\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124034ORa0tYNDvLC7SUHT.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2013 春季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124034Fdv9ZE74IsnwT0mq.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2012 秋季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124035rDQe7VMsWwBm3RiJ.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124035kNwI75BlzxiUL0QP.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2012 春季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124036M6wJdIlSLVKqOWg7.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2011 秋季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124036sYZ2yObu3GfD7NXC.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2011／2010 春季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124037lWIXPV9wR2eD1CgE.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2010 春季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021240370tcvB5XopIkUTDFb.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2009 秋季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124038xj4bCGndhFDrBY2z.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2009 秋季／早秋系列\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124038cFvUdQY4pmn73qzu.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2009 春季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021240392UXESRCqofu1KOms.jpg\" width=\"644\" height=\"488\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75776398\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2008 秋季／春季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124039JLDdWhzPaKM9AfNV.jpg\" width=\"644\" height=\"488\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75776398\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2006 秋季／2007 春季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124040U4lwSt2ARqcvh3uZ.jpg\" width=\"644\" height=\"488\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75776398\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2006 秋季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021240408m7CXhjw1UVKRzoQ.jpg\" width=\"404\" height=\"308\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76237624\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t2004 秋季／2005 春季\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124041plh6vwuX5gtQO2s9.jpg\" width=\"604\" height=\"308\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5